<title>SINGAPORE: Hotel Plaza first-half net jumps 115 pct.</title>
<headline>Hotel Plaza first-half net jumps 115 pct.</headline>
<dateline>SINGAPORE 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to June 30, 1996</p>
<p>		   (in millions of S$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Net profit			     4.90  vs   2.28</p>
<p>    Group shr (cents)		    1.23  vs   0.57</p>
<p>    Turnover				81.68  vs  55.97</p>
<p>    Other income incl. interest	2.11  vs   2.28</p>
<p>    Interest (expense)		  10.40  vs   7.17</p>
<p>    Depreciation (expense)	     8.17  vs   6.56</p>
<p>    Pre-tax profit			 7.82  vs   3.26</p>
<p>    Loss from associates		 0.17  vs   0.13</p>
<p>    Tax					2.25  vs   1.51</p>
<p>    Minorities		    (loss) 0.50  vs   0.67 (gain)</p>
<p>Note - Full name is Hotel Plaza Ltd.</p>
<p>-- Singapore newsroom (65 8703199)</p>
</text>
